<b><font color="#800000">Install pbdR Image</font></b>


<ol>
<li>
Download the pbdR image which is available at
<a href="https://drive.google.com/file/d/0B9DZ_BJKFAAJMFp1NUV0WU5laUU/edit?usp=sharing" target="_blank">Google Drive</a> (1.7GB).
<br>
<br>

<li>
Open installed Virtual Box.
<br>
<img src="./figures_vm/pbdr_01.png" align="top">
<br>
<br>

<li>
Click on the File menu and the "Import Appliance..." option.
<br>
<img src="./figures_vm/pbdr_02.png" align="top">
<br>
<br>

<li>
Click on "Open appliance..." button to select the pbdR image.
<br>
<img src="./figures_vm/pbdr_03.png" align="top">
<br>
<br>

<li>
Select the pbdR image (pbdr_xubuntu-13.10_img.ova) downloaded from
<a href="https://drive.google.com/file/d/0B9DZ_BJKFAAJMFp1NUV0WU5laUU/edit?usp=sharing" target="_blank">Google Drive</a> (1.7GB).
Note that the previous version (xubuntu-13.04*.vba) is used in the next picture.
<br>
<img src="./figures_vm/pbdr_04.png" align="top">
<br>
<br>

<li>
Click on the Next button to obtain the pbdR image information.
<br>
<img src="./figures_vm/pbdr_05.png" align="top">
<br>
<br>

<li>
Click on the Import button to import the pbdR image to the VirtualBox.
<br>
<img src="./figures_vm/pbdr_06.png" align="top">
<br>
<br>

<li>
Wait for a few minutes.
<br>
<img src="./figures_vm/pbdr_07.png" align="top">
<br>
<br>

<li>
Done.
<br>
<img src="./figures_vm/pbdr_08.png" align="top">
<br>
<br>

</ol>
